snp1.9:153:
153"Ajja pannaraso uposatho, Dibbā ratti upaṭṭhitā;
		Anomanāmaṁ satthāraṁ,
		Handa passāma gotamaṁ".

snp1.9:154:
154 "Kacci mano supaṇihito, Sabbabhūtesu tādino;
		Kacci iṭṭhe aniṭṭhe ca,
		Saṅkappassa vasīkatā".

snp1.9:155:
155 "Mano cassa supaṇihito, Sabbabhūtesu tādino;
		Atho iṭṭhe aniṭṭhe ca,
		Saṅkappassa vasīkatā".

snp1.9:156:
156 "Kacci adinnaṁ nādiyati, Kacci pāṇesu saññato;
		Kacci ārā pamādamhā,
		Kacci jhānaṁ na riñcati".

snp1.9:157:
157 "Na so adinnaṁ ādiyati, Atho pāṇesu saññato;
		Atho ārā pamādamhā,
		Buddho jhānaṁ na riñcati".

snp1.9:158:
158 "Kacci musā na bhaṇati, Kacci na khīṇabyappatho;
		Kacci vebhūtiyaṁ nāha,
		Kacci samphaṁ na bhāsati".

snp1.9:159:
159 "Musā ca so na bhaṇati, Atho na khīṇabyappatho;
		Atho vebhūtiyaṁ nāha,
		Mantā atthañca bhāsati".

snp1.9:160:
160 "Kacci na rajjati kāmesu, Kacci cittaṁ anāvilaṁ;
		Kacci mohaṁ atikkanto,
		Kacci dhammesu cakkhumā".

snp1.9:161:
161 "Na so rajjati kāmesu, Atho cittaṁ anāvilaṁ;
		Sabbamohaṁ atikkanto,
		Buddho dhammesu cakkhumā".

snp1.9:162:
162 "Kacci vijjāya sampanno, Kacci saṁsuddhacāraṇo;
		Kaccissa āsavā khīṇā,
		Kacci natthi punabbhavo".

snp1.9:163:
163 "Vijjāya ceva sampanno, Atho saṁsuddhacāraṇo;
			Sabbassa āsavā khīṇā,
			Natthi tassa punabbhavo".

snp1.9:168:
168 "Kismiṁ loko samuppanno, Kismiṁ kubbati santhavaṁ;
		Kissa loko upādāya,
		Kismiṁ loko vihaññati".

snp1.9:169:
169 "Chasu loko samuppanno, Chasu kubbati santhavaṁ;
			Channameva upādāya,
			Chasu loko vihaññati".
